                            <property name="valign">start</property>
                            <property name="label" translatable="yes">You can use Fly-Pie to launch applications, simulate hotkeys, open URLs and much more. This interactive tutorial will teach you how to use Fly-Pie most efficiently. Click the big button below to open a training menu!</property>
